subject: JavaDoc of container types
msgSnippet: Hi folks, Just a gentle suggestion that when javadoc ing you specify the actual concrete classes expected to be found in container classes. IE errors public
messageBody:
Hi folks,

Just a gentle suggestion that when javadoc'ing you specify the
actual concrete classes expected to be found in container classes.

IE

errors
public java.util.Enumeration errors()

Returns an Enumeration for the errors


(An enumeration of what?)

Thanks
